author: leosimons
msg: dtds/: import the xhtml 1.1 spec and the xhtml-modularization spec on which the 1.1 spec depends. These specs come from the W3C, see http://www.w3.org/. Putting them in SVN allows setting up an XML catalog using these, which will make validation go faster.
